                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 Council/4–1447: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Smith</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-04-14T17:00:00+03:00"
                            >April 14, 1947—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received April 14—10:41 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1344. Delsec 1420 for Acheson from Marshall. Your Secdel 1453 refers. I have
                    reconsidered the matter in the light of your suggestions and do not wish to make
                    a reply to Molotov’s letter. [Marshall.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Smith</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
